title: From here to there
description:
FROM HERE TO THERE

Rip by: LneTra

	
FROM HERE TO THERE is a documentary that follows best friends and professional freerunners Cory DeMeyers and Jesse La Flair on their 2013 International Freerunning and Parkour Tour. This is the story about their journey to become top athletes and break down boundaries in the fastest growing action sport in the world. Featuring interviews and appearances by top athletes in Freerunning and Parkour, this is an inside look into Freerunning and Parkour as told by the Pros.
